fish_clipboard_paste | string join + | math
.EE
.UNINDENT
.UNINDENT
.IP \(bu 2
\fBstatus fish\-path\fP returns a fully\-normalised path, particularly noticeable on NetBSD (#9085 \%<https://\:github\:.com/\:fish-shell/\:fish-shell/\:issues/\:9085>).
