Performance improvements to highlighting (#9180 \%<https://\:github\:.com/\:fish-shell/\:fish-shell/\:issues/\:9180>) should make using fish more pleasant on slow systems.
.IP \(bu 2
On 32\-bit systems, globs like \fB*\fP will no longer fail to return some files, as large file support has been enabled.
