.IP \(bu 2
A new \fBAstronaut\fP prompt (#8775 \%<https://\:github\:.com/\:fish-shell/\:fish-shell/\:issues/\:8775>), a multi\-line prompt using plain text reminiscent of the Starship.rs prompt.
