.SS Improved prompts
.INDENT 0.0
.IP \(bu 2
The \fBfish_status_to_signal\fP helper function returns the correct signal names for the current platform, rather than Linux (#8530 \%<https://\:github\:.com/\:fish-shell/\:fish-shell/\:issues/\:8530>).
.IP \(bu 2
The \fBprompt_pwd\fP helper function learned a \fB\-\-full\-length\-dirs N\fP option to keep the last N directory components unshortened. In addition the number of characters to shorten each component should be shortened to can now be given as \fB\-d N\fP or \fB\-\-dir\-length N\fP\&. (#8208 \%<https://\:github\:.com/\:fish-shell/\:fish-shell/\:issues/\:8208>):
