An unhelpful error (\(dqaccess: No error\(dq), seen on Cygwin, is no longer produced (#7785 \%<https://\:github\:.com/\:fish-shell/\:fish-shell/\:issues/\:7785>).
.IP \(bu 2
Improvements to the \fBrsync\fP completions (#7763 \%<https://\:github\:.com/\:fish-shell/\:fish-shell/\:issues/\:7763>), some completion descriptions (#7788 \%<https://\:github\:.com/\:fish-shell/\:fish-shell/\:issues/\:7788>), and completions that use IP address (#7787 \%<https://\:github\:.com/\:fish-shell/\:fish-shell/\:issues/\:7787>).
.IP \(bu 2
Improvements to the appearance of \fBfish_config\fP (#7811 \%<https://\:github\:.com/\:fish-shell/\:fish-shell/\:issues/\:7811>).
