numeric operations on invalid integers (#3346 \%<https://\:github\:.com/\:fish-shell/\:fish-shell/\:issues/\:3346>, #3581 \%<https://\:github\:.com/\:fish-shell/\:fish-shell/\:issues/\:3581>).
