working correctly on these platforms under UTF\-8 locales; fish now
avoids the buggy behaviour (#3050 \%<https://\:github\:.com/\:fish-shell/\:fish-shell/\:issues/\:3050>).
.IP \(bu 2
Prompts which show git repository information (via
\fB__fish_git_prompt\fP) are faster in large repositories (#3294 \%<https://\:github\:.com/\:fish-shell/\:fish-shell/\:issues/\:3294>) and
slow filesystems (#3083 \%<https://\:github\:.com/\:fish-shell/\:fish-shell/\:issues/\:3083>).
