are given (#139 \%<https://\:github\:.com/\:fish-shell/\:fish-shell/\:issues/\:139>)
.IP \(bu 2
History files are stored under the \fBXDG_DATA_HOME\fP hierarchy (by
default, in \fB~/.local/share\fP), and existing history will be moved
on first use (#744 \%<https://\:github\:.com/\:fish-shell/\:fish-shell/\:issues/\:744>)
.UNINDENT
.SS Other notable fixes and improvements
.INDENT 0.0
.IP \(bu 2
Fish no longer silences errors in config.fish (#2702 \%<https://\:github\:.com/\:fish-shell/\:fish-shell/\:issues/\:2702>)
.IP \(bu 2
Directory autosuggestions will now descend as far as possible if
there is only one child directory (#2531 \%<https://\:github\:.com/\:fish-shell/\:fish-shell/\:issues/\:2531>)
.IP \(bu 2
Add support for bright colors (#1464 \%<https://\:github\:.com/\:fish-shell/\:fish-shell/\:issues/\:1464>)
.IP \(bu 2
